npx lint-staged

# As requested, fetch covers and strip metadata before commit.
# lint-staged handles metadata stripping on staged files.
# fetch-covers needs to run globally as it might fetch new covers.

node scripts/fetch-covers.mjs
node scripts/remove-dangling-images.mjs

# If fetch-covers modified files, add them to the commit?
# The user said "before any commit and push".
# If valid, they should be staged. But git hooks shouldn't automagically add unstaged files usually.
# However, for "fetch-covers", if it downloads a new cover, we probably want it in the commit.
# Let's add any changes in public/media to the staging area if they were modified by fetch-covers.
git add public/media
